<description>
Protects the server from CSRF attacks by filtering out&#xa; web requests and verifying against a csrf token generated per&#xa; session.&#xa; &lt;p&gt;&#xa; To secure your servlet from a CSRF attack, configure this filter&#xa; in web.xml of the web module to protect against particular http methods.&#xa; &lt;p&gt;&#xa; Example: Protects FileServet PUT and POST requests from CSRF attacks&#xa; &lt;p&gt;&#xa; &lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;&amp;#xa; &amp;lt;filter&amp;gt;&amp;#xa;  &amp;lt;filter-name&amp;gt;csrfProtectedFileFilter&amp;lt;/filter-name&amp;gt;&amp;#xa;  &amp;lt;filter-class&amp;gt;javax.baja.web.filters.CsrfProtectedFilter&amp;lt;/filter-class&amp;gt;&amp;#xa;  &amp;lt;init-param&amp;gt;&amp;#xa;    &amp;lt;param-name&amp;gt;httpMethod&amp;lt;/param-name&amp;gt;&amp;#xa;    &amp;lt;param-value&amp;gt;PUT,POST&amp;lt;/param-value&amp;gt;&amp;#xa;  &amp;lt;/init-param&amp;gt;&amp;#xa; &amp;lt;/filter&amp;gt;&amp;#xa; &amp;lt;filter-mapping&amp;gt;&amp;#xa;  &amp;lt;filter-name&amp;gt;csrfProtectedFileFilter&amp;lt;/filter-name&amp;gt;&amp;#xa;  &amp;lt;url-pattern&amp;gt;/file/*&amp;lt;/url-pattern&amp;gt;&amp;#xa; &amp;lt;/filter-mapping&amp;gt;&amp;#xa; &lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
</description>
